### Secure Copy -rp recurse and preserve modification times


REMOTE to LOCAL
$ scp your_username@remotehost.edu:foobar.txt /some/local/directory

LOCAL to REMOTE
$ scp foobar.txt your_username@remotehost.edu:/some/remote/directory

# to local station
scp -i ~/.ssh/id_rsa root@hostname.net:/tmp/SPECjvm2008-bare.7z /tmp

#from local station to hostname.net:/tmp
scp -i ~/.ssh/id_rsa SPECjvm2008-bare.7z root@hostname.net:/tmp
